Passive is always active during night battles. [Active]: Increases the damage dealt to all enemies by 18% for 6 seconds.

skills.Name: Shockwave Explosion
skills.Description: Throws a grenade 5 units ahead of self that deals 3x damage to enemies within a 2.5 unit radius and inflicting a knockback effect of 3 units. If self is in the middle row, enemies are knocked to the sides; If self is in the top/bottom row, enemies are knocked to the middle of the battlefield. The knockback effect is ineffective against enemies in the middle of attacking or using skills.

skills.Name: Symmetrical Adjustment
skills.Description: Increases damage by 55% for 5 seconds. While skill is active, prioritise enemies that are within 5 units range of self and deal additional 10% damage to them.

skills.Name: Blazar
skills.Description: [Passive]: When attacking enemies ahead of self, increases damage by 20%. [Active]: Increases damage by 65% and prioritise the closest enemy ahead for 5 seconds.

skills.Name: Perfect Chain
skills.Description: [Passive]: After each reload, grants +1 ammo to other machine guns in the echelon and reduce self reload time by 20%, up to 60% max. [Active]: Immediately complete a special reload and obtain +8 additional ammo. When using additional ammo, increases damage and accuracy by 50%.

skills.Name: Assault Focus
skills.Description: Increases rate of fire by 60% for 5 seconds.

skills.Name: Nightfire
skills.Description: [Passive]: Deals 0.2x dummy-link-ignoring damage to the attacked target in a 1.5 unit radius. [Active]: During night battles, prioritize targets which have not attacked yet, checking enemies for 5 seconds. Enemies damaged by this skill have their evasion decreased by 90% for 3 seconds. (Stacks once, can only be used during night.)

skills.Name: Intersecting Support
skills.Description: Grants a 32 HP shield to the T-Doll in the leader position; increases the damage of the remaining T-Dolls by 22% for 8 seconds.

skills.Name: Tactical Taunting
skills.Description: [Passive]: For every 20% max HP lost, grants self a 20 HP shield. [Active]: Reduces incoming damage taken by 20% and grants self a 'Taunt' effect for 8 seconds. [Taunt]: Enemies' basic attacks and strengthened attacks will prioritize targets with 'Taunt' within attack range.

skills.Name: Double Guard
skills.Description: Increase self damage by 20% of self accuracy before skill activation for 5 seconds. The first 3 attacks after skill activation deal 2 hits.

skills.Name: Ode to the Dawn Carnival
skills.Description: [Passive]: For every stat reduction effect on self, increase final damage by 5% (stacks additively). [Active]: Swaps to Focus mode, reducing self rate of fire by 20%, movement speed and evasion by 30%; Increases self damage by 35%, accuracy by 60%, critical damage by 50% for 5 seconds.

skills.Name: Assault Focus
skills.Description: Increases damage by by 15%, rate of fire by 30% and accuracy by 80% for 5 seconds.

skills.Name: Cognitive Transformation
skills.Description: Activate the skill to switch between modes: [Offense Focused]: Every 0.1 seconds, converts own evasion into both damage and accuracy. Every -1 point of evasion is converted to +2 points of damage and +1 points of accuracy. Conversion stops when evasion is lower than 75. [Evasion Focused]: Every 0.1 seconds, converts own damage and accuracy into evasion. Every -1 points of damage and accuracy is converted into +4 points of evasion. Conversion stops when damage is lower than 35 or accuracy is lower than 23. Stat changes from either conversion is applied after other stat modifiers, and converted stats will not disappear as a result of other modifiers expiring. After changing modes, prioritize restoring the converted stats first.

skills.Name: Shared Hatred
skills.Description: [Passive]: At the start of battle, summon 3 reinforcement T-Dolls with 3 dummy links each to the rear of the echelon. Each reinforcement has 5 HP per dummy link and inherits the following stats from General Liu; 35% damage, 60% rate of fire and 40% accuracy. The remaining stats and targeting mode are also the same as General Liu. [Active]: Activate the skill to switch between the following modes; [Rear-Focus (default)]: Reduces own rate of fire by 10% and increases own damage by 20% and target sthe furthest enemy from self. [Vanguard Focus]: Reduces own damage by 10% and increases own rate of fire by 20% and targets the nearest enemy from self.

skills.Name: Conviction of Certain Victory
skills.Description: [Passive]: If currently assigned as an echelon's leader, permanently reduces own rate of fire by 35% while increaing allied Rifle's critical hit rate by 20% and critical hit damage by 10%. [Active]: When skill is activated, allies on her tiles gain 15% damage and 12% rate of fire for 5 seconds. [EQ Passive]: When equipped with 'Old Camoflage Uniform', does not reduce own rate of fire when assigned as the echelon's leader.

skills.Name: Destructor Intrusion
skills.Description: [Passive]: Obtains +1 stack of 'Destruct' every second. For every stack of 'Destruct' currently active, increases own final damage by 2.5% up to a max of 10 stacks. [Active]: Consumes all stacks of 'Destruct' and obtains damage/accuracy/rate of fire equivalent to teh stat of the enemies with the highest respective stat. The stat gain is capped at 45% of self damage, 80% of self accuracy and 40% of self rate of fire. The effect lasts for 6 seconds and no stacks of 'Destruct' can be gained throughout the skill's duration.

skills.Name: Spreading Bloodthirst
skills.Description: [Passive]: During reloading state, allies on her tiles gain 20% evasion, whereas allies not on her tiles gain 10% damage. [Active]: Extends the current volley by +12 ammo. When using additional ammo, increases own accuracy by 80% and extends the next reload time by 4 seconds.

skills.Name: Rapid Firing
skills.Description: Begin charging after skill cooldown ends, gaining 1 charge stack every second, up to a maximum of 5 stacks. When skill is used, shoot the current target thrice, dealing 1.7 ~ 3.2x damage per shot based on the current number of charge stacks, taking 0.5 seconds to aim before each shot. All stacks will be consumed on skill use.

skills.Name: Rotating Magazine
skills.Description: Upon skill activation, the next 2 reloads have their reload time reduced to 0 seconds. Attacks after the first reload have 90% increased damage. Attacks after the second reload have 150% increased accuracy.

skills.Name: Sharpshooting
skills.Description: [Passive]: If there are enemies near self, switch to knife mode. In this mode, every attack will deal 0.25x damage 4 times to the nearest target that cannot miss. [Active]: Fire 4 consecutive shots with perfect accuracy at the current target, with each hit dealing 6x damage and ignores HP shields. Every shot requires 1 second of timing.

skills.Name: Opposites Repel
skills.Description: [Passive]: Reduces damage dealt to self from enemies directly ahead by 20%. [Active]: Performs an attack that does not deal damage, forcibly knocking back moveable enemies within a 150-degree frontal cone of 6 unit radius ahead of self by 5 units, and remove the targets' HP shields and buff effects. Additionally, increases self armor by 20% for every target knocked-back (up to 5 stacks max) and reduce self damage by 0% for 8 seconds.

skills.Name: Resilience of Blood and Fire
skills.Description: [Passive]: The first attack will consume all ammo and deal 4 hits. Whenever ammo is fully used up, switches to RF mode and change targeting mode to prioritise the furthest enemy from self. While RF mode is active, obtains the following stat changes: Reduced evasion by 10%, increased rate of fire and damage by 100%, increased accuracy by 200%, increased armor piercing by +100 points. [Active]: Reload and switches back to SG mode. Grants self a taunt effect until SG mode ends. Reload time is fixed at 2 seconds. When reloading ends, remove stat changes from RF mode and gains a 75HP shield for 5 seconds. (Slug ammo only applies to normal attacks under SG mode)

skills.Name: Survival First
skills.Description: [Passive]: Whenever movement is made, grants self +9 movement speed which gradually decays within 9 seconds. [Active]: Gains additional evasion equal to 0.8x of armor value for 4 seconds.

skills.Name: Fiery Dimension
skills.Description: [Passive]: When reloading, reduce the remaining skill cooldown time by 20% for self and other shotguns in the same column. [Active]: Upon skill activation, increases own armor and evasion by 20% for every shotgun in the echelon for 6 seconds.

skills.Name: Griffin Command
skills.Description: For every allied two/three-star rarity T-Dolls on the field, increase said T-Dolls' damage, rate of fire, accuray, evasion, and armor by 5% for 8 seconds. The buff increases based on the number of two/three-star T-Dolls present, up to a max of 25%.

skills.Name: Complex Modification
skills.Description: When skill is activated, grants effects based on the number of allies present on their buff tiles; If there is more than 2 allies present, increases damage by 15% for 2 seconds to self and allies on their tiles. If there is 2 or less allies present, increases evasion by 40% for 2 seconds to self and allies on their tiles.

skills.Name: Candy Echo
skills.Description: [Passive]: When changing attack targets, inreases own damage by 10% for 5 seconds (stacks up to 4 layers). [Active]: For 5 seconds, each attack from every enemy dummy link carries an additional 150 points of fixed damage, ignoring enemy evasion, armor and HP shields; When attacking enemies wiht multiple dummy links, the effect is doubled.

skills.Name: Snake-Nest Hunting
skills.Description: Increases own damage by 40% for 15 seconds. While skill is active, for every layer of damage buffs obtained, increases own rate of fire by 5% until the skill ends (stacks up to 8 layers).

skills.Name: Hummingbird Resonance
skills.Description: [Passive]: Gain +1 Hummingbird every 2 seconds. If there are no allied unit sin the same column at the start of battle, gain +3 Hummingbirds instantly. Can hold up to 9 Hummingbirds. For every Hummingbird possessed, self attack inflicts an additional 1x damage. [Active]: Consume all Hummingbirds and grant buffs to the entire team that last for 8 seconds. During the skill, no new Hummingbirds will be gained. [1/2/3 Hummingbirds consumed]: Increase all allies' damage by 9%/16%/25%. [4/5/6 Hummingbirds consumed]: On top of existing effects, increase all allies' rate of fire by 5%/12%/25%. [7/8/9 Hummingbirds consumed]: On top of existing effects, increase all allies' critical hit rate by 20%/50%/100%.

skills.Name: Covert Killer
skills.Description: [Passive]: Normal attacks fire 2 bullets, dealing 0.5x damage twice. If both bullets hit, deal additional damage equal to 5% of the enemy's lost HP (capped at 5x of self damage). [Active]: Increase damage dealt by each bullet to 1x. Additional damage dealt is increased to 10% of the enemy's lost HP (capped at 5x of self damage). During the skill, attacks against enemies with less than 50% HP will never miss. The skill lasts for 5 seconds.

skills.Name: Adaptive Suppression
skills.Description: [Passive]: Attacks against enemies inflict an amplifying debuff that increases damage received by 3% for 8 seconds, stacking up to 5 layers. After 6 seconds, the debuff inflicted from attacks are doubled. [Active]: Activate the skill to switch between the following modes; [Strafing mode (default)]: Attack 2 enemies, dealing 1.2x damage each. Prioritize enemies that have not been attacked yet. [Secure mode]: Deal 1.2x damage twice to the same enemy. The first hit will have perfect accuracy.

skills.Name: Hunting Time
skills.Description: [Passive]: At battle start, select a random target as prey. After participating in killing the prey, increase self damage by 45% and accuracy by +6 points. When the prey dies, select another random enemy as prey. [Active]: Immediately target the enemy with the highest HP as prey and attack them until that unit dies. While skill is active, every attack increases self damage by 1%, stacking up to 5 layers and lasting until the current prey dies or the skill ends. The skill lasts for 5 seconds.

skills.Name: Matryorshak Tactics
skills.Description: [Passive]: When receiving DMG/ROF/EVA/ACC/CRIT buffs (including fairy talents), reduce current cooldown by 20%. Can only be activated once every skill cooldown. [Active]: Permanently increases damage by 10%. The 3rd activation also increases rate of fire by 15%. The 5th activation also increases accuracy by 30%. Can be activated up to 6 times.

skills.Name: Firepower Union
skills.Description: [Passive]: For every ally in the same column, increase own damage and accuracy by 15%, stacking up to 2 layers. [Active]: Increases all allies' damage by 22% for 8 seconds.

skills.Name: Silent Marking
skills.Description: [Passive]: Whenever a dummy link deals a critical hit, add +1 layer of Marking on the target, stacking up to 15 layers. When an enemy reaches 15 layers of Marking, remove the enemy's HP shield and any evasion or armor increasing effects, and reduce its evasion and armor by 50% for 5 seconds. This effect can only be triggered once per target. [Active]: Increase all allies' critical hit rate by 15%. Additionally, enemies with Marking receive +3% more damage taken per layer of Marking. Effects last for 5 seconds.

skills.Name: Electroshock Gear
skills.Description: [Passive]: Increase own damage dealt to targets under abnormal status by 20%. Normal attacks prioritize enemies under abnormal status. At the start of battle, gain 3 Taser charges. Gain +1 additional Taser charge evey 10 seconds (can store up to 5). [Active]: Consume 1 Taser charge and deal 3x damage to the nearest enemy with perfect accuracy. Additionally, apply the following effects to the target and enemies behind the target: stun the targets for 3 seconds and reduce their rate of fire and movement speed by 30% for 6 seconds (duration reduced by half against elite enemies).

skills.Name: Teddy Bear Frontline
skills.Description: [Passive]: Allied SG on self tiles obtain position fortification effect; When receiving damage, place a teddy bear ahead of self that taunts enemies. This effect can be triggered once evey 15 seconds for every unit, and the teddy bear inherits 5% Max HP, 50% evasion, and 50% armor of that unit. Each teddy bear lasts for 5 seconds. [Active]: Activate the skill to switch between the following modes; [Continuous mode (Default)]: Reduce own damage and accuracy by 10% and increase attack interval by 10%. No reloading is required while in this mode. [Burst mode]: Increase own critical hit rate by 20% and critical hit damage by 40% and attack the target with the highest HP. Every 4th hit will deal double damage.

skills.Name: Polar Night Flash
skills.Description: During nighttime, increases her damage and critical hit damage by 70% (28% during day) for 8 seconds. Additionally, if there are 3 or more gun types on the field, increase critical hit rate by 30% (Does not apply during day battles).

skills.Name: Rho Aias
skills.Description: [Passive]: When there are 2 or more SMGs in the echelon, grants a 50 HP shield to the echelon at battle start and reduce initial skill cooldown by 15%. [Active]: Reduce the damage stat of enemies within an area of 6 units ahead by 20, lasting for 8 seconds.

skills.Name: Pel's Mission
skills.Description: After battle start, the Bulldog Pel joins the fight, inheriting the following stats from KH2002; 600% damage, 80% rate of fire, 200% accuracy. This unit cannot be targeted, cannot crit and is unaffected by aura effects. When KH2002 retreats, Pel also retreats. KH2002's final damage is reduced by 0% until the end of the battle.

skills.Name: Dance With Me
skills.Description: When there are 3 or more ARs in the echelon, increase self damage by 40%. When receiving damage buffs, increase the echelon leader's damage by 50% of the current multiplicative damage buffs on self for 4 seconds. This effect cannot trigger other skill effects.

skills.Name: Time Reversal
skills.Description: [Passive]: When there are 3 or more ARs in the echelon, increase critical hit rate of allies within 1 tile of self by 25%. [Active]: Record the stats of the ally with the current highest DPS, and return 110% of the recorded stats to that ally after 6 seconds. This effet lasts for 6 seconds. Within the effect period, the target's stats will be constantly overwritten by the recorded stats. This effect cannot trigger other skill effects.

skills.Name: Get Drunk
skills.Description: Prioritize the enemy with the highest base damage. Can continune firing after running out of ammo, and only reloads when self DPS is the highest among all allies. Every attack increases self critical hit rate by 3% for 4 seconds, stacking up to 12 layers.

skills.Name: Interlude Division
skills.Description: Alternates between 'Advance State' and 'Suppression State' aura effects. Defaults to Advance State when skill is first activated. [Advance State]: During nighttime, increases all allies' damage by 35% (20% during daytime) for 8 seconds (in both day and night). [Suppression State]: During nighttime, decreases all enemies damage by 40% (25% during daytime) for 8 seconds (in both day and night).

skills.Name: Embezzlement Negotiations
skills.Description: Marks the target with the current highest HP and prioritize attacking it for 3 seconds (prioritizes bosses if they are present). For 3 seconds, self attacks will have perfect accuracy, guaranteed critical hits and bypass armor. After 3 seconds, if the marked target is still on the battlefield, inflict a 25% amplification debuff on the target while applying a Taunt effet onto it which causes friendly units to target it, lasting 5 seconds. If the marked target dies or vanishes, all allies' remaining skill cooldowns are reduced by 25%.

skills.Name: Cometary Wildfire
skills.Description: Minimum attack interval is 1 second, prioritizes armored enemy units and does 2x damage to them. Rests for 5 seconds every 5 stacks. Damage to armored units is increased by 100%

skills.Name: Katyusha
skills.Description: Depending on current skill level, T-Dolls in the echelon carrying an [AK] are enhanced; [AK-74M]: All T-Dolls wielding an AK in the echelon gain 5% damge and rate of fire. [AK-47]: 'Raid Focus' damage and accuracy buffs are swapped. [AK-74U]: 'Repulsive Response' is buffed to a passive. [AK-12]: 'Eye of the Snow Wolf' grants an additional 35% critical hit damage while it is active. [AK-15]: Attacks will always trigger her 'Anger' effect. [AK-Alfa]: Has perfect accuracy when targeting enemy units in front of her. The following T-Dolls effects will be active; AK-74M, AK-47, AK-74U, AK-12, AK-15, AK-Alfa.

skills.Name: Boundary Starburst
skills.Description: At battle start, if there are other shotguns in the same column, grant perfet accuracy to self and knockback chance increases to 10%. Whenever an enemy is hit by an attack, increase self Activeness by 1 point. When Activeness hits 100 points, deal fatal damage to the non-elite enemy unit with the highest damage stat. Thereafter, increase self damage by 75%, attack interval becomes fixed at 1 second and self no longer reloads, lasting until the end of the battle.

skills.Name: Cheese Coagulase
skills.Description: [Passive]: Becomes immune to damage 5 points or lower. [Active]: Deal dummy-link damage with perfect accuracy that ignores armor equal to 6x of self armor to enemies 2 units ahead of self. Additionally, machine guns within the rearmost column gain 90% incoming damage reduction for 10 seconds.
